normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645e34049efc63f4a18963dbadfe04d2690880c5","tid":114623,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失緊業 <br />\n搵工會唔會成功 同埋份工好唔好pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThanks樓主</blockquote><br />\n2卦3爻  凶位黎 你腳踏實地搵位普通既工好啲<br />\n強求啲唔洗做又好待遇既工會愈來愈差"},{"pid":"2903fd22ebdb026eaf616382a1ef02dbd73ab689","tid":114623,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排比種慢性疾病纏身 好多醫生都睇過 但都無乜效 遲啲六月要返大陸個半月 想問下六月之前好唔好得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝樓主</blockquote><br />\n我占易經同彿卡都話你有好轉<br />\n但要休養多啲 好翻左都要小心身體"},{"pid":"97caa0d67efb97300c8395eb1e7543fa2ccdf985","tid":114623,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉行順利嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n47卦6爻 你依家個人都幾擔心未來<br />\n暫時唔太順利 原因係你未睇清楚形勢<br />\n6爻本身應該要靜待 而你依個時候轉行時唔好 工唔好<br />\n轉到你都會後悔 亦可以話你想轉既工唔係幾啱你<br />\n可以再等多排先轉"},{"pid":"d2a27d436a644a7d3666c8444c46cceabf30f8d9","tid":114623,"uid":55303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"幾時有拖拍"},{"pid":"9817697749975621932abb549b7225c93077e7e0","tid":114623,"uid":81248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"唔係好鐘意而家份工，無咩心機做落去。好想出黎自己闖下，做自己事業。下唔到決心去做呢件事，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係唔係時候？"},{"pid":"f0278d8dc136fdcb8567abf4f693a0b02e55e7d8","tid":114623,"uid":58356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:56:05.000Z","msg":"想問我前途點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚遲啲變廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm